                        "name": "peptolab",
                        "displayName": "Simon Mundy",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Does this happen with all messages or only some? Can you provide a little more detail on how you construct a message, along with a message body that you know that fails?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=peptolab",
                        "name": "peptolab",
                        "displayName": "Simon Mundy",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-04-12T18:07:40.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-04-12T18:07:40.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/14181",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=till",
                        "name": "till",
                        "displayName": "Till Klampaeckel",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "It happens with all messages, here is how I get $mail:\n\n{code}\n$mail = new Zend_Mail();\n$mail->setSubject('Neuer Kommentar');\n\n$message  ='Es gibt einen neuen Kommentar auf Ihrer Homepage.';\n$message .=\"\\n\\n\";\n$message .='Klicken Sie auf den folgenden Link, um zu dem Kommentar zu gelangen:';\n$message .=\"\\n\\n\";\n$message .=$comment_url;\n$message.= \"\\n\\n\";\n$message.= \"-- \\nmail robot\";\n\n$mail->setBodyText($message);\n$mail->setFrom('noreply@mydomain.de', 'Mail Robot);\n$mail->addTo($to_email, $to_name);\n{code}\n\n\nThis is weird though, because the exact same code works in production. I was always thinking that this is a connectivity issue with the mailserver but I can not trace the problem. As I said in my initial report, the server is working and reachable from this web server. No connectivity issues what-so-ever.\n\nObviously all variables (such as $to_email, $to_name, $comment_url, ...) are set.\n\nThanks for looking into it!",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=till",
                        "name": "till",
                        "displayName": "Till Klampaeckel",
                        "active": true
                    },
